SUMMARY
============================================================
  All subgroup analyses use full-sample OW weights (downstream).
  Balance checked within each subgroup (max_smd column).

  Files:
    etables_4_5_subgroups.csv — surgery, MDS, age, baseline Mg, PPI/diuretic/eGFR
    etable6_safety.csv — ICU LOS, vent, HR, max Mg, IABP/ECMO

  Key predictions:
    Mg <2.0 effect > Mg >=2.0 → 'repletion benefits the depleted'
    Age >=60 effect > Age <60 → age-related Mg depletion
    MDS >=2 effect > MDS 0-1 → composite risk guides therapy
    Safety null across the board → 'no harm at these doses'

